{
  "stem": "25639.11",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was-- there were about four inmates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the lady was screaming because she was pregnant when she arrived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was a newlywed, and she didn't know that she was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so she didn't show it, show her pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after about three months, she began to show.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so, apparently there was an underground in this area as well because they wanted to save her life, and take her baby away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I learned that the l-- one of the ladies there was Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Gisi.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody called her Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Gisi, whom I was to meet later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] then finally, the wom-- they told her that, you should give up this baby.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And someday, someday when we get out of this hellhole, that you and your husband will meet, and you can have another child.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But if you don't consent to this, both you and your baby will be murdered, as you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so finally, she consented.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she cried very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I actually-- I woke up to that, before the process started.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that, of course, became of interest to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How could anybody go back to sleep after that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, I watched the procedure as they took her baby away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She, with her bare hands, reached in and, and aborted the pregnancy so that the woman could live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many, many years later, just a few years ago-- maybe about 10, 15 years ago-- I was looking into some paper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was an advertisement in it that I-- about a book which said, And I decided to send for that book because it was the Shaare Zedek hospital in Jerusalem that put the ad in into the bulletin, and-- the Jewish bulletin in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 46
    }
  ],
